pan style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;8</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何陈述竞选词？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;9</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做述职报告？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;10</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何接受媒体访问？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">……</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: white; background: red;">【课程收益】</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、减少上台恐惧</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、弄懂讲稿设计</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">3</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、学会故事演说</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">【