<p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: white; background: red;">【课程背景】</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">马云在</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">6</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">分钟内说了什么使其获得了</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">2000</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">万美元的投资？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">说什么话会让孩子自然喜欢你、被你领导？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">王石说了什么让下属都把心放在企业上？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">面对员工，如何描绘梦想，陈述使命，凝聚人心？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">面对政府，如何展现企业精神，赢取政府支持？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">面对对手，如何灵活应付，让对手肃然起敬？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">任何企业家都在运营过程中，都需要运用语言的智慧去说服别人，领导者都需要自己的想法能得到充分的执行，企业家只有依靠演说智慧的力量、才能在商海中纵横捭阖、化解危机；在企业内部统一思想、凝聚人心！</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">销售，引爆财富；演说，征服世界！</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: white; background: red;">【课程大纲】</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;1</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做绩效动员？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做婚礼主持？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;3</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做嘉宾介绍？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;4</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何致开闭幕词？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;5</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做年度总结？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;6</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做婚礼祝辞？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;7</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何致领颁奖词？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;8</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何陈述竞选词？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;9</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做述职报告？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;10</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何接受媒体访问？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">……</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: white; background: red;">【课程收益】</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、减少上台恐惧</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、弄懂讲稿设计</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">3</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、学会故事演说</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">【