<p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: white; background: red;">【课程背景】</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">马云在</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">6</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">分钟内说了什么使其获得了</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">2000</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">万美元的投资？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">说什么话会让孩子自然喜欢你、被你领导？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">王石说了什么让下属都把心放在企业上？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">面对员工，如何描绘梦想，陈述使命，凝聚人心？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">面对政府，如何展现企业精神，赢取政府支持？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">面对对手，如何灵活应付，让对手肃然起敬？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">任何企业家都在运营过程中，都需要运用语言的智慧去说服别人，领导者都需要自己的想法能得到充分的执行，企业家只有依靠演说智慧的力量、才能在商海中纵横捭阖、化解危机；在企业内部统一思想、凝聚人心！</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">销售，引爆财富；演说，征服世界！</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: white; background: red;">【课程大纲】</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;1</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做绩效动员？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做婚礼主持？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;3</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做嘉宾介绍？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;4</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何致开闭幕词？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;5</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做年度总结？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;6</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做婚礼祝辞？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;7</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何致领颁奖词？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;8</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何陈述竞选词？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;9</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何做述职报告？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;10</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、如何接受媒体访问？</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">……</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: white; background: red;">【课程收益】</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、减少上台恐惧</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、弄懂讲稿设计</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">3</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">、学会故事演说</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">【师资介绍】</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px;">导师</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">—</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 21px; line-height: 31.5px;">王风范</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">►</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">陆演者工坊创始人</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">►</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">微演说系统创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">►</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">微辞理论的提出者、实践者</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">►</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">国家一级注册培训师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">►</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">华人企业资本路演首选教练</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">►</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">赢家讲堂及倍增讲堂栏目《微演说》系列主讲人</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">►</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">畅销书《总裁演说》《微演说》《微沟通》《资本路演》系列的作者</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">►</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">清大、厦大、交大等知名学府</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">EMBA</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">总裁班导师</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">►</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">被媒体誉为</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">“</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">微时代里唯一讲话最少却让你收益最多的演说教练</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">”</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">近</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">7</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">年中内训过的企业有：</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">中国平安、中国人寿、中国太平洋、安康振兴实业集团、安康阳光车城、淄博大亚金属、上海巨易地产、无锡培正教育、巴州讯通公司、库尔勒时光传媒、米泉红太阳商贸、安徽恒大投资集团、陶然居大酒店、北园春大酒店、鸿瑞大酒店、杭州中涛控股、云南临沧市教育局、山西兴县教育局、张家口电信、杭州为诚医药、新疆伊犁酒业、无锡世嘉盛集团、立邦集团、中国红太阳集团、上海缪氏集团、德国杜塞尔多夫集团、上海申通地铁、上海香雪海国际、浦东燃气销售公司，上海烟草、中国航空八院、中国兴业银行等数百家企业。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p>

